A non-invasive tool for detecting cervical cancer odor by trained scent dogs.

Guerrero-Flores H(1), Apresa-García T(2), Garay-Villar Ó(3), Sánchez-Pérez A(4), 
Flores-Villegas D(4), Bandera-Calderón A(5), García-Palacios R(6), Rojas-Sánchez 
